Package: jsonl-viewer
Version: VERSION
Architecture: all
Maintainer: jorjives
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, gir1.2-gtksource-5
Description: GNOME JSONL viewer with syntax highlighting
 A two-pane viewer for JSONL/NDJSON files. Browse entries in a sidebar,
 inspect formatted JSON with syntax highlighting, and right-click any
 key to use it as the sidebar label. Supports file watching for live
 tail of streaming logs.
